parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Goodyear run-flat tires can lead to a loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Bubbles or bulges on the sidewall of the tire
tire failure
sudden loss of air pressure
and vibration while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The drivetrain malfunction can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or jerk, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The drivetrain malfunction warning light comes on
the vehicle loses power
stalls
or jerks
and the engine may overheat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the CV joint can cause the vehicle to lose propulsion, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The CV joint boot is torn or leaking
the vehicle shakes or vibrates
and the drivetrain malfunction warning light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The throttle lag can cause the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle creeps out slowly from a stop
then jumps forward quickly and unexpectedly
and the transmission may not downshift as needed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The powertrain issues can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or jerk, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
stalls
or jerks
and the engine may overheat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls
the fuel gauge is inaccurate
the vehicle has a reduced power mode
the check engine light is on
the vehicle has an extended crank time
and there is a fuel odor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An inaccurate fuel gauge can lead to the vehicle running out of fuel, causing the vehicle to stall and potentially leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The fuel gauge is inaccurate
the vehicle runs out of fuel
and the fuel gauge does not indicate the correct fuel level.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of recall repairs can lead to the vehicle continuing to operate with a known safety defect, potentially causing accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle has a known safety defect
the recall repair is delayed or unavailable
and the vehicle is not repaired in a timely manner.
